reviewText: Amazingly good! As allways Marisa know what she is doing and delivered a very touching concert that left me in tears sometime. Love it!!!

The music selection and the scenario arrangements were absolutely astonishing. However the best part of the concert was choosing an string quintet to perform in parallel with the band. What a beautiful combination!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! Perhaps her best performance yet. .
Exactly what you'd expect from Marisa and nicely produced
